  {
    "date": "2026-04-21 08:09",
    "weekly_narrative": "本週全球市場進入「荷姆茲海峽震盪期」，地緣政治引發的能源成本上升與 AI 電力需求共振，推升 WTI 原油來到 86.21 美元，進一步強化通膨粘性。儘管 DXY 美元指數小幅回落至 98.074，但美國十年期公債殖利率仍固守在 4.250% 高位，反映出市場對「更高、更久」利率環境的畏懼。金價受避險情緒支撐衝上 4842.8 美元新高，而比特幣在資金多元化配置下企穩於 7.5 萬美元上方。整體市場在經濟衰退風險與結構性通膨之間拉鋸。",
    "next_week_forecast_html": "<details class='analysis-container'><summary>📢 下週預測：能源通膨與避險資產的強勢拉鋸</summary><div class='analysis-content'><strong>⛓️ 市場邏輯傳導：</strong><p>荷姆茲海峽緊張 ➔ 影響<strong>油價與能源通膨</strong> ➔ 推升<strong>美債殖利率維持 4.250%</strong> ➔ 最終支撐<strong>黃金與比特幣避險買盤</strong>。</p><hr><strong>📉 資產動態預測：</strong><ul><li><strong>亞洲貨幣 (TWD/JPY/KRW)：</strong>面臨油價帶來的經常帳壓力，亞幣回升幅度受限，央行干預風險增加。</li><li><strong>避險成本與鋼鐵業：</strong>隨金價衝上 4842.8，避險成本高企，基建與傳產在通膨壓力下利潤空間遭壓縮。</li></ul></div></details>",
    "focus_html": "\n        <div class=\"focus-card\">\n            <div class=\"focus-idx\">01</div>\n            <div class=\"focus-content\">\n                <h4>荷姆茲海峽衝擊與通膨連鎖反應</h4>\n                <p>歐央行總裁拉加德警告，荷姆茲海峽局勢將導致歐洲面臨長期供應鏈衝擊，這與油價 86.21 的走勢相呼應。能源價格的上漲直接推升全球通膨預期，使得債市殖利率在 4.250% 附近難以下行。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"focus-card\">\n            <div class=\"focus-idx\">02</div>\n            <div class=\"focus-content\">\n                <h4>AI 轉型與勞動力市場的結構性矛盾</h4>\n                <p>市場正辯論 AI 是否導致 20% 的失業率或產能大幅提升。這種結構性轉變在標普 500 指數 7109.14 的點位中得以體現，科技成長與傳統就業替代的焦慮情緒交織，影響長線增長動能。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
    "fx_rates_linkage": "當前 DXY 位元於 98.074，呈現盤整回軟態勢。主因在於荷姆茲危機迫使亞洲與歐洲央行展現更強硬的鷹派立場以支撐匯率。然而，美國 4.250% 的殖利率維持了美德/美日利差，限制了美元下行空間。高油價同時惡化了非美能源進口國的貿易帳，資金流向實物黃金與比特幣避險。",
    "tbody_html": "\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">🔥 通膨預期</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">CPI/PPI Outlook</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">結構性粘性 <span class=\"status_detail\">能源與 AI 電力成本疊加</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">持續攀升</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">荷姆茲海峽局勢、WTI 原油 86.21、AI 數據中心電費攀升</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">📉 利率預期</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">Fed Funds / US10Y</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">高位拉鋸 <span class=\"status_detail\">US10Y 報 4.250%</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">高點盤整</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">就業市場矛盾、通膨回落受阻、ECB 鷹派預期</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">🦅 美元指數</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">DXY Strength</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-down\">盤整回軟 <span class=\"status_detail\">DXY 報 98.074</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-down \">緩步回落</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">非美央行防禦性轉鷹、比特幣資產替代（BTC 75781.3）</td>\n                </tr>",
    "risk_html": "\n        <div class=\"risk-item\">\n            <span class=\"risk-title\">⚠️ 能源供應鏈斷裂風險</span>\n            <p class=\"risk-content\">若荷姆茲封鎖時程超預期，WTI 原油可能突破 90 大關，引發全球滯脹危機。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"risk-item\">\n            <span class=\"risk-title\">⚠️ 亞洲央行政策兩難</span>\n            <p class=\"risk-content\">面對通膨輸入與本幣貶值，亞洲央行可能被迫超預期升息，衝擊區域房地產與股市穩定。</p>\n        </div>",
    "news_html": "\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMihgFBVV95cUxPMW43SEFlUkk0NUdQRG5kTkNJWElsRHgwTktoMTNNYWEtUlJxY0xia1RWOWdGTmpkSFdFdFpwNDI1YWZfbDB1U0lWNzlwczJvU0RFOGJnYnNJa1lTMUZpSFQxUzNGNmxjSzRUVU9xdzl6QTVxZHMyMGU5aW43Tl9VRUxmY1ZBZw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Oil Prices, the General Price Level and Inflation - Haver Analytics</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMic0FVX3lxTE54RW11OGFEb1J3bmFjLXZfV2tkM3d6aXRGMy1IcW5hNV9iQ2w2YTJKQUE2YW1XZ3lldWhSU0hCRnFtU1ZFRmVvQ1Bwa2dQWkgyeHhvWGRIb1hlampBVzM2blhvWDcyMld6RjB1clVrY1VrY1k?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 How to cope with losing your job and make unemployment suck a little less - vox.com</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiswFBVV95cUxQc3c0WDhPVy1MdWlubk8wd21lS3RiQ0VLaEVwcHQ1Mmpfc25JUUJPS3hyLWR6Uzh6SWpXYTBHZzkzN2JfUjE0M2FJZUExY19WYzk2QVFhSEE1OWlNVk5hM2RNQkJqbUhuend4M3lpMzRCc3dRNEluT3hLOHZkOE8yZV9VYm5JaTA5bEtzUHIySXdDMHhRd05xdUpkLVI1TkFGaldvZ3RydWR2NXlackdQQmJFMA?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 ECB chief Lagarde warns Europe faces prolonged fallout from Hormuz shock - Anadolu Ajansı</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Is AI going to lead to 20% unemployment - or just make your employees superhuman? - Insurance Business</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMisAFBVV95cUxQdVd6UXJKMXoxbVlKam1fby1mN09FZXNKelhZaWtoS1FUZHJKZnZxdnpqX1g4bXhWQVMxa2xlWEtmcnNaOXJ1ZEJxemo1eWotZnhUek54cmxmZjFlU3Zqd015RkthWVVSSWVVR1BSTEtUYkhEQVFKNEFqU043cWgtWDhzQ2xxZjVoNnpmelNxYWlLV1VuVzFDdWNlTUxPVGZ3ZUZSRjBueVF4X3VTT2wwVA?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Asia Economic Monthly: Asian Central Banks’ Hormuz Dilemma - Nomura Connects</a>\n                </li>",
