  {
    "date": "2026-04-20 14:32",
    "weekly_narrative": "本週全球市場呈現「結構性通膨與地緣政治」雙重壓力下的震盪格局。隨著中東局勢持續動盪，市場對於降息的預期進一步推遲。標普 500 指數雖然維持在 7126.06 點的高位，但面臨美國十年期公債殖利率 4.246% 的強大壓制。最顯著的變動在於避險資產的重新定價，美元指數 DXY 跌至 98.303 的支撐位，資金顯然正從傳統貨幣轉向實物資產與去中心化資產，推升金價至 4813.3 美元，比特幣則盤整於 7.4 萬美元上方。整體情緒處於「通膨粘性」與「經濟衰退擔憂」的拉鋸戰中，AI 驅動的能源需求正取代傳統週期，成為推升成本的新主因。",
    "next_week_forecast_html": "<details class='analysis-container'><summary>📢 下週預測：中東局勢與通膨數據的二次衝擊</summary><div class='analysis-content'><strong>⛓️ 市場邏輯傳導：</strong><p>地緣政治衝突擴大 ➔ 影響<strong>能源供應與避險情緒</strong> ➔ 最終定價<strong>金價維持高位與美元區間震盪</strong>。</p><hr><strong>📉 資產動態預測：</strong><ul><li><strong>亞洲貨幣 (TWD/JPY/KRW)：</strong>隨美元指數在 98.303 附近波動，亞幣將維持區間盤整，需關注各國央行是否跟進鷹派發言。</li><li><strong>避險成本與鋼鐵業：</strong>原油 82.59 美元與金價 4813.3 美元的高掛，將持續推升製造業成本，利潤率可能受限。</li></ul></div></details>",
    "focus_html": "\n        <div class=\"focus-card\">\n            <div class=\"focus-idx\">01</div>\n            <div class=\"focus-content\">\n                <h4>中東戰雲與降息預期的脫鉤</h4>\n                <p>南非央行行長警告，中東戰爭帶來的動盪已嚴重陰影化降息前景。這使得即使經濟數據放緩，各國央行在抑制通膨與防止衰退間陷入兩難，全球利率維持高位運行的時間將超乎預期。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"focus-card\">\n            <div class=\"focus-idx\">02</div>\n            <div class=\"focus-content\">\n                <h4>AI 勞動力與能源需求的結構轉型</h4>\n                <p>市場正熱議 AI 是否會導致 20% 的失業率或造就「超人級」員工。然而，更直接的衝擊在於 AI 電力需求對能源供應鏈的壓力，這正支撐原油價格維持在 82.59 美元，並成為結構性通膨的核心因子。</p>\n            </div>\n        </div>",
    "fx_rates_linkage": "美元指數 DXY 目前報 98.303，反映出市場對非美央行（如 RBA 或 SARB）維持鷹派的預期。由於通膨具備粘性，美國 10 年期公債殖利率守在 4.246%，這本應支撐美元，但避險資金流向更具抗通膨屬性的黃金 (4813.3) 與比特幣 (74481.72)，導致美元吸引力邊際遞減。這對於緩解新興市場匯率壓力有正面作用，但高借貸成本依然抑制了標普 500 的續漲動能。",
    "tbody_html": "\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">🔥 通膨預期</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">CPI/PPI Outlook</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">結構性粘性 <span class=\"status_detail\">AI 電力需求取代傳統循環</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">持續攀升</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">AI 電力與能源轉型成本、地緣政治推升油價至 82.59。</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">📉 利率預期</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">Fed Funds / US10Y</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-up\">高位拉鋸 <span class=\"status_detail\">US10Y 報 4.246%</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-up \">緩慢下行受阻</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">經濟衰退擔憂與粘性通膨之間的債市拉鋸戰。</td>\n                </tr>\n                <tr>\n                    <td data-label=\"核心變數\">\n                        <div class=\"var-name\">🦅 美元指數</div>\n                        <span class=\"badge\">DXY Strength</span>\n                    </td>\n                    <td data-label=\"當前狀態\"><div class=\"status trend-down\">盤整回軟 <span class=\"status_detail\">DXY 報 98.303</span></div></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"趨勢\"><span class=\"trend-down \">橫盤偏弱</span></td>\n                    <td data-label=\"驅動因素\" class=\"desc-text\">非美央行鷹派、資產多元化（比特幣破 7.4 萬）。</td>\n                </tr>",
    "risk_html": "\n        <div class=\"risk-item\">\n            <span class=\"risk-title\">⚠️ 能源價格二次通膨風險</span>\n            <p class=\"risk-content\">若中東局勢惡化導致原油衝破 90 美元，將徹底瓦解目前的降息預期，並推升公債殖利率進一步上揚。</p>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"risk-item\">\n            <span class=\"risk-title\">⚠️ 債券市場的定價錯誤</span>\n            <p class=\"risk-content\">目前市場在衰退與通膨間搖擺。若殖利率因通膨失控而飆升，可能引發股市估值的大幅修正。</p>\n        </div>",
    "news_html": "\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiwgFBVV95cUxNaW14SE1jZFpoUHZzQWVEX3h0QzVRVFoxQ3hYWE9TS3hTTzRIMkdaT01UQWIzdDI5UU5jR0lOdVoyS3hJZ29VNlR6RGxleDBKMzJNeHRtc2JfRHM0MXZScnZ4NjlndkUyeE5NeVhpdDh6TDROLXJCcjdkWUw3VGpNUjFKUTNtcS1VYk9jQUdkZzZ5dHhKYUNwSnM0N3ZQRTlaWWxEb1QzNXdseUJHRkJ5WGF2WlBmZTRqRUhqd1dyU1ZhUQ?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 The RBA’s policy deliberately creates unemployment. So why do we treat the jobless so badly? - The Conversation</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Is AI going to lead to 20% unemployment - or just make your employees superhuman? - Insurance Business</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Middle East war turmoil clouds rate cut prospects, South Africa central bank chief says - Reuters</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMisgFBVV95cUxQaGs5U1FBaVdzb2NKQ1M2ZXVrMUNYUlNIRTF0VXRmS1RRUlRYZ1lPNFBMUEVOWmhnM0h5UmZSOEZLYW9YcjhhTV9Wb2t3amlGdmV6dThuM1hRbFVZVzN6d1ZrWU9DNkJfSVd1ek9HcGoxQ2x5eHk0dE1vZDJoZUFZbDRiNU1fUHh2UnhoSkh6YVBJNS1JYTJnSnp3VTNVS1FTLU03R1ZQOG1KTUJfR2d2aWlR?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Inflation or recession? The tug of war in bond markets - The Economist</a>\n                </li>\n                <li class=\"news-item\">\n                    <a href=\"https://news.google.com/rss/articles/CBMiZkFVX3lxTE1PcmdpYzdnSTBWckxQM0FmcmxiNUYzWW9Va2hlQ3B0d0R2THp1ZXpMMU9yeTlCak5OY3V6aHhycUE4NVlHZEVqUDB6eGIzcXJjNC1La1VwT3YzVjFmODVxRXJ3V05NZw?oc=5\" target=\"_blank\">📄 Inflation, deflation, and the “Goldilocks scenario” - Britannica</a>\n                </li>",
